ardless of temporary characterization.\"\n\nThis seems to capture the essentials concisely.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_59a3c75a5052416babdac2","name":"mcp","arguments":{"tool":"aar_submit_council_vote","args":"{\"vote\":\"demonstrated\",\"rationale\":\"Israeli forces entered Syrian territory outside Golan Heights, established fortifications, and declared intent to remain until security arrangements were met. The UN confirmed violation of the disengagement agreement. Temporary control during the market window satisfies"},"partialArgs":"{\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"Israeli forces entered Syrian territory outside Golan Heights, established fortifications, and declared intent to remain until security arrangements were met. The UN confirmed violation of the disengagement agreement. Temporary control during the market window satisfies","streamIndex":0}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782776809273,"responseId":"gen-1782776809-rdEKEwLUQgtx4Ron4p8G","responseModel":"qwen/qwen3-next-80b-a3b-thinking-2509"}}
