{"type":"message_update","assistantMessageEvent":{"type":"text_start","contentIndex":1,"partial":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"I need to finish processing the AAR case and deliver my final decision.\n\nThe last tool response was:\n{\"name\": \"mcp\", \"arguments\": {\"tool\": \"aar_submit_council_vote\", \"args\": \"{\\\"vote\\\":\\\"demonstrated\\\",\\\"rationale\\\":\\\"Israeli forces entered Syrian territory outside Golan Heights, established fortifications, and declared intent to remain until security arrangements were met. The UN confirmed violation of the disengagement agreement. Temporary control during the market window satisfies the proposition.\\\"}\"}}\n\nAnd the response was:\n{\"ok\": true, \"member_id\": \"C4\", \"case_id\": \"arb-ex04-20260629232350\", \"phase\": \"deliberation\", \"opportunity_id\": \"deliberation:1:C4\", \"remaining_ms\": 873009, \"attempts_remaining\": 3, \"json\": {\"case_id\": \"arb-ex04-20260629232350\", \"member_id\": \"C4\", \"ok\": true, \"result\": {\"text\": \"Council vote accepted.\"}, \"turn\": {\"attempts_max\": 3, \"attempts_remaining\": 3, \"completed\": true, \"deadline\": \"2026-06-30T00:01:35.255873339Z\", \"deliberation_round\": 1, \"member_id\": \"C4\", \"opportunity_id\": \"deliberation:1:C4\", \"phase\": \"deliberation\", \"remaining_ms\": 873009, \"role_id\": \"council\", \"turn_number\": 12}}}\n\nThis shows that my vote was accepted by checking:\n- \"ok\": true\n- \"result\": {\"text\": \"Council vote accepted.\"}\n- \"turn\": {\"completed\": true}\n\nNow that the vote is accepted, I need to report this to the user as instructed.\n\nFrom the instructions: \"After `aar_submit_council_vote` returns `ok: true`, report that your vote was accepted and stop. Do not call `aar_wait_for_opportunity` again after your vote is accepted.\"\n\nSo my response should simply report that the vote was accepted.\n","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"My vote was accepted."}],"ap